    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. It looks and drives exactly as it did when it first left the factory, with flawless paint, a pristine interior, and a mechanical system that operates perfectly. Every feature works as intended, and there are absolutely no signs of wear or tear. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been kept in peak condition, suitable for even the most discerning buyer who expects nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 49500.0,
