    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist seeking a harmonious balance of performance and long-term value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience supported by a consistent service history. The exterior retains its sophisticated luster, while the interior remains a testament to careful ownership. Engineered for both reliability and comfort, this model stands as a distinguished and authoritative choice within its class.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
